# GetFit Docker Configuration

This file contains environment variables for the Docker Compose setup.
Copy this file to `.env` and update the values before running docker-compose.

## Database Configuration
DB_PASSWORD=postgres

## Backend Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your_secure_jwt_secret_change_this_in_production
APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

## Email Configuration
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password

## Frontend Configuration
API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api

## Production Notes:
## - Change DB_PASSWORD to a strong password
## - Generate a secure JWT_SECRET (use: openssl rand -base64 32)
## - Update APP_URL to your production domain
## - Configure EMAIL_USER and EMAIL_PASSWORD for email functionality
## - Update API_URL to match your production backend URL
